    "excerpt": "Yakov Green shares a short <em>kavvanah</em> (intention, meditation) which he wrote in Hebrew one morning at <a href=\"http://www.elul.org.il/\">Beit Midrash Elul</a> in Jerusalem. He later translated it into English. תפילת דרך משולשת | Triple Prayer for the Road . . .",
    "content": "<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Hebrew</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">English</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nכשאני נתקל בצומת, אני מתפלל<br />\nשאבחר בדרך נכונה.<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nWhen I encounter a crossroads, I pray<br />\nTo choose a correct path.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nכשאני בוחר בדרך, אני מתפלל<br />\nשהיא תוביל אותי למקום נכון.<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nWhen I choose a path, I pray<br />\nIt will lead me to a correct place.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nכשאני מגיע לסוף דרך, אני מתפלל<br />\nשלא יהיה סוף לדרך.‏<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nWhen I reach a path&#8217;s end, I pray<br />\nThe path will have no end.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<p>Yakov Green shared the short <em>kavvanah</em> (intention, meditation) which he wrote in Hebrew one morning<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Written Wednesday, March 23, 2011&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_